Learning Objective one point three,

59
00:02:15,540 --> 00:02:18,210
which requires you to be able
to describe the key concepts

60
00:02:18,210 --> 00:02:21,070
of service relationships,
including service offerings,

61
00:02:21,070 --> 00:02:22,720
service relationship management,

62
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:25,260
service provision, and
service consumption.

